author: Marie J. French
title: Cuomo says more ventilators inbound from China, Oregon
description: “Stop the virus here. It’s better for the state of Oregon, it’s better for the nation," Cuomo told reporters Saturday.
content:
Andrew Cuomo | AP Photo
ALBANY, N.Y. The Chinese government is sending New York 1,000 ventilators and Oregon is shipping another 140 to help respond to the state's ballooning number of Covid-19 patients that has sent political leaders hustling for equipment,… [+3235 chars]
